dialog.body: Hello, thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Christopher Mitchell. May I have your name please?
Nice to meet you, Catherine. Can you please provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is two five zero zero three seven.
Thank you, Catherine. Additionally, could you confirm your date of birth for security reasons?
My date of birth is zero four dash one zero dash nineteen eighty-five.
Great, thank you for the information, Catherine. Is there anything specific you need assistance with regarding your policy today?
I wanted to inquire about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
Of course, I can assist you with that. Let's go ahead and get the details of your new vehicle. Thank you for your time, Catherine.
